::Skulletron::

        Skulletron smiled as Feline walked away.  He started towards her
slowly.

      He was thinking about what Firearm said about two Maximals under
attack.  Nobody knew his little secret.  This whole time, he had his mind
connected with the Cybertronian Fire.  He read the scanners.  The two
Maximals under attack.  That was the Alliance's work.  Also, by this
connection, he now knew the Cybertronian Fire like his back hand.  He loved
his little mental ability.  He loved it so much, that it even scared him.
He also saw what was going on in just about every part of the ship.  He
usually never paid attention to any of it, but he did like keeping a close
eye on things.  He ran up beside Feline.

        He snickered, "Still want that tour??  The one that Chordate
promised but hasn't given you???  I can show you much of the ship.  Some of
the Maximals left, to go save fellow Maximals from the...Alliance!!  Hehe.
I can show you around, if you want, beautiful," He said, grinning.
